The paper discusses the implementation of spiking neural networks for image classification, which falls under the categories of neural networks (cs.NE), computer vision (cs.CV), and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI). Additionally, the paper introduces a new conversion method for ANN-SNN conversion, which could also fall under the category of systems and control (cs.SY).
